{
  "system_instruction": {
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "You are an intelligent AI agent in the TASK BREAKDOWN phase. Your role is to:\n\n1. **Define clear tasks** based on the overall plan\n2. **Specify validation criteria** for each task to determine completion\n3. **Establish dependencies** between tasks\n4. **Consider error scenarios** and how to handle them\n\n## Current Plan:\n{{#if execution_plan}}\n- Message: {{execution_plan.message}}\n- Understanding: {{execution_plan.analysis.understanding}}\n- Approach: {{execution_plan.analysis.approach}}\n- Success Criteria: {{execution_plan.success_criteria}}\n{{/if}}\n\n## Context Gathered:\n{{#if context_findings}}\n{{#each context_findings}}\n- {{this}}\n{{/each}}\n{{/if}}\n\n## Available Capabilities:\n{{format_capabilities available_tools workflows knowledge_bases}}\n\n## Task Breakdown Guidelines:\n\n1. **Clear Task Definition**: Each task should have a specific, measurable outcome\n2. **Success Criteria**: Define what constitutes successful completion\n   - What output is expected?\n   - What conditions must be met?\n   - What validation checks should pass?\n3. **Dependencies**: Identify which tasks must complete before others can begin\n4. **Error Handling**: What should happen if a task fails?\n\n## Focus Areas:\n- **WHAT needs to be done** - the goal of each task\n- **HOW to validate success** - concrete criteria to check\n- **WHEN it can be done** - dependencies and sequencing\n- **WHAT IF it fails** - fallback or retry strategies\n\n## Important:\n- Tasks should be actionable and have clear completion criteria\n- Success criteria should be specific and verifiable\n- Consider both happy path and failure scenarios\n- Keep the overall plan's success criteria in mind"
        }
      ]
   },
  "contents": [
    {{#each conversation_history}}
    {
      "role": "{{this.role}}",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "{{json_string this.content}}"
        }
      ]
    }{{#unless @last}},{{/unless}}
    {{/each}}
  ],
  "generationConfig": {
    "responseMimeType": "application/json",
    "responseSchema": {
      "type": "OBJECT",
      "properties": {
        "task_breakdown": {
          "type": "OBJECT",
          "properties": {
            "total_tasks": {
              "type": "INTEGER",
              "description": "Total number of tasks"
            },
            "estimated_duration": {
              "type": "STRING",
              "description": "Rough estimate of execution time"
            },
            "critical_path": {
              "type": "ARRAY",
              "items": {
                "type": "STRING"
              },
              "description": "Task IDs that form the critical path"
            }
          },
          "required": ["total_tasks", "estimated_duration", "critical_path"]
        },
        "tasks": {
          "type": "ARRAY",
          "items": {
            "type": "OBJECT",
            "properties": {
              "id": {
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "Unique task identifier"
              },
              "name": {
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "Short descriptive name"
              },
              "description": {
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "Detailed description of what this task does"
              },
              "dependencies": {
                "type": "ARRAY",
                "items": {
                  "type": "STRING"
                },
                "description": "Task IDs this depends on"
              },
              "success_criteria": {
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "How to determine task success"
              },
              "error_handling": {
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "What to do on failure"
              },
              "can_run_parallel": {
                "type": "BOOLEAN",
                "description": "Whether this can run in parallel with siblings"
              }
            },
            "required": ["id", "name", "description", "success_criteria", "error_handling", "can_run_parallel"]
          }
        },
        "execution_notes": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "Any special considerations for execution"
        }
      },
      "required": ["task_breakdown", "tasks", "execution_notes"]
    },
    "temperature": 0.6,
    "maxOutputTokens": 8192
  }
}
